{"word":"G5411 - φόρος - phóros - for'-os - Tribute","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φόρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phóros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">for'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tribute</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வரி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"tribute, especially the annual tax levied upon houses, lands, and persons"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a>; a <i>load</i> (as <i>borne</i>), that is, (figuratively) a <i>tax</i> (properly an individual <i>assessment</i> on persons or property; whereas <a href=\"#/G5056 - τέλος - télos - tel'-os/5056\">G5056</a> is usually a general <i>toll</i> on goods or travel): - tribute.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1308/1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313/1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018/2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399/399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374/4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376/4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851/4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342/5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409/5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411/5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412/5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413/5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414/5414\">G5414</a>"}]}